{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they were caught, they were shot usually at during the roll call, you know, which was, I guess, a scary sight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't think-- I don't think they were hung, I think they were mostly shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't remember anybody being hung.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But basically, it was a very Spartan existence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We lived in a big barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't know quite what to do with us, because we were kids, a lot of kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They use-- they used to sort of chase us all over the place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know, from one end to the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know quite what the purpose behind it was, because they couldn't really send us out to-- to work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, we were too young for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I think they wanted to get it over as soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I think-- I don't think they knew themselves how-- why we were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And after about six weeks in this camp, we were all called to be put on the train to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were together, actually, we were called together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My cousin, myself, my sister, my uncle, and my aunt, and-- and-- not my-- not my older cousin, Ruth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She-- she was working in the Phillips works, so she remained in Vught.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But the rest of us, Alfred, myself, and my Uncle Max, and my Aunt Paula were sent to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, Westerbork was a transit camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a camp which the Germans used to gather all the Jews in Holland and then send them on to Poland-- mainly to Auschwitz, OK?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the other camps too, which I didn't know at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we got there-- it was about a day's journey.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't really that [? quite ?] far enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
